        "id": "9c48dcbb297244d2c4983e0c"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "As a result, I've ordered a mass evacuation has been issued to all Aurigan military and civilians still capable of reaching Coromodir.\n\nAll JumpShip and DropShips are ordered to assist in the evacuation efforts.",
