        "id": "9cf971c4e2c2dfafaed6f9e7"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "In Coromodir we will create a redoubt and make our last stand in our capital to defeat these raiders and expel them from our worlds.\n\nFor the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAuriganReach],Aurigan Reach]]!",
