        "id": "9cedd529350bc4cd0b29a247"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Based on the reports that we saw from [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHeliat],Heliat]], [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGangtok],Gangtok]] and other locations, it's become apparent to Lady Arano and the rest of the Founding Council that it is impossible to defend all of the Reach.",
