        "id": "9c401f0d76b4d0ea6b56a35f"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Wait... and [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCoromodir],Coromodir]]?\n\nIs it even possible to defend Coromodir or are we risking everything there?",
