      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Of course, Commander, but Yang has a point, since we'll lose air superiority really quick once the <i>Orion's Belt</i> arrives.\n\nAnd [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreEspinosasCoup],last time]] we had to escape from Coromodir... well we got lucky, as we all remember.",
