        "id": "9cf6a08021ddc9f8f0c1e6ff"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Kamea also made no announcement regarding her uncle, Director Espinosa, so it's doubtful they have captured him.\n\nWhich means that the situation at Coromodir might not be fully controlled by the [[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganRestoration],Restoration]] at this point.",
      "branches": [
